    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Ginkgo biloba are tinnitus, which is alleviated by its anti-inflammatory properties, memory loss due to its ability to improve blood flow to the brain, and macular degeneration, a condition that Ginkgo biloba has been shown to slow down by protecting the retina from oxidative damage. Additionally, poor circulation is improved by Ginkgo biloba's vasodilatory effects, while cognitive decline is treated by its antioxidant properties that protect brain cells from damage. Dizziness and vertigo are also relieved by Ginkgo biloba's ability to improve balance and equilibrium through its effects on the inner ear. Furthermore, Ginkgo biloba has been found to be effective in treating varicose veins by improving blood flow and reducing inflammation, and it has also been shown to slow down the progression of Alzheimer's disease by reducing oxidative stress and inflammation in the brain. Other ailments that Ginkgo biloba has been found to alleviate include glaucoma, impotence, erectile dysfunction, Raynaud's disease, migraines, anxiety, fatigue, multiple sclerosis, and headaches.",
